{"title":"给毛少贤的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给毛少贤的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1954年4月28日）少贤同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年十二月的信收到，感谢你的好意。眼病以就近医治为宜，出外不容易。此复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝健康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年四月廿八日[1]毛少贤，毛泽东的远房亲属。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":4,"day":28}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":85,"page_end":85}